# READ ME

## Simple script to automate the creation of bash projects

! Check the `create-bash-project-config.json` to make sure all your paths exist !

## Basic call would be

`create-bash-project projectname`

Gives you a basic folder structure

projectname/
├── projectname - this is the main script \ bash file
├── installer - run this to copy the main script to `~/bin` and make it executable
├── config.json - values used in the project - data logging etc
├── READ_ME - Blank readme